# Comments API

## Create a comment
POST http://localhost:4000/comments HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "offerId": "5f0f5f3f3f3f3f3f3f3f3f3f",
  "authorId": "ed3eihduwehfdwefwefwefwef",
  "text": "This is a comment",
  "rating": 5
}

###

## Get all comments
GET http://localhost:4000/comments/5f0f5f3f3f3f3f3f3f3f3f3f HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
